metadata.name: DDC Coin #1
metadata.description:
DDC Coins are special rewards sent out to the holders of Demon Death Cult: Season 1 NFTs.

In total there will be 5 different coins in this collection, with each new coin being sent out on the first day of each month to anyone holding a demon from Season 1.

If you collect and hold all 5 coins, you will receive a valuable, special, mystery gift on October 1st and December 25th of 2022.

If you continue hold your 5 coins past that date, there will be more future rewards announced in 2023.

If you arrived too late to DDC to receive an older coin as a free airdrop, you can try to buy one on the marketplace.

Join the Discord community and read the FAQ channel for more information here: https://discord.gg/ddc

Follow the project on Twitter: https://twitter.com/demondeathcult
